title: Dreamcast SNES Emulation cdi Image Set
description:
Compressed file contains the following:


(1)  DreamsnesA2F.cdi (Romsets A to F, Dreamsnes emulator included)

(2)  DreamsnesG2M.cdi (Romsets G to M, Dreamsnes Emulator Included)

(3)  DreamsnesN2Z.cdi (Romsets N to Z, Dreamsnes Emulator Included)


(4)  Snes.cdi (Includes 903 romsets A to Z with Dreamsnes Emulator Included)


Additional Instructions:

"Image kits 1 through 3: each  cdi image can fit on "1" blank CD-R disc."

Image kit (4) has to be burned on a high density CD-R disc in order for the burn to be successful, which means the blank CD-R has to have more then 700mb of disc space for this image file.


Burn these images using Discjuggler or Bootdreams.
These Image files were created with the DREAMCAST FACTORY!!

Enjoy and please Seed everyone.!
